01:27:03.386 --> 01:27:06.856
*

01:27:06.889 --> 01:27:08.989
- He got scared.

01:27:09.024 --> 01:27:11.264
- Of what?

01:27:11.294 --> 01:27:14.664
- Of everything.

01:27:14.697 --> 01:27:15.997
Of failing!

01:27:16.031 --> 01:27:17.471
Failing to provide,

01:27:17.500 --> 01:27:19.570
failing to be vital,
compelling,

01:27:19.602 --> 01:27:23.812
failing to make you pregnant.

01:27:23.839 --> 01:27:26.709
You know, it's easy to be cocky
when you're 20,

01:27:26.742 --> 01:27:28.842
but I don't feel that way
anymore.

01:27:28.877 --> 01:27:31.447
- Well, who does?

01:27:31.480 --> 01:27:34.750
Jesus, you're in
the shit-or-shut-up years.

01:27:34.783 --> 01:27:43.533
*

01:27:43.559 --> 01:27:45.429
So what do you see?

01:27:50.766 --> 01:27:55.336
- I create exactly what I fear.

01:27:55.371 --> 01:27:57.671
- Yeah, I can see that.

01:28:02.110 --> 01:28:04.010
- What do you see?

01:28:13.088 --> 01:28:16.058
- I'm disappointed.

01:28:18.494 --> 01:28:20.904
I'm really disappointed.

01:28:23.599 --> 01:28:25.469
I mean, I could dig in at work
and be happy.

01:28:25.501 --> 01:28:27.701
I could.

01:28:27.736 --> 01:28:32.066
But I don't want that.

01:28:32.107 --> 01:28:35.477
I want it at home with you,

01:28:35.511 --> 01:28:37.881
